Boris used to believe in aliens, but then he took an arrow to the knee.
Boris has visited almost every parallel dimension to kill off the Borises there. There can be only one.
The universe ponders the great mysteries of Boris.
He who fights with Boris should be careful lest he thereby become Boris.
If the abyss gazes long into Boris, he will also gaze into the abyss.
Beauty is in the eye of the Boris.
Talent hits a target no one else can hit; genius hits a target no one else can see. Boris hits a target even he can't see.
Boris can only be understood backwards; but he must be lived forwards.
Freedom is what we do with what is done to us by Boris.
